  "2026-04-01T12:03:33.389Z",cursor-agent,"Implemented graceful exit handling in src/cli/main.ts catch path: replaced forced process.exit(...) calls with process.exitCode assignment plus early return to preserve existing exit-code mapping while allowing buffered output to flush naturally. Validation evidence: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts tests/integration/cli.integration.spec.ts passed (56/56)."
